  "texts": [
    "We chose to examine time as a proxy for effort.",
    "We subset the data to humans and conducted another EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT mixed model analysis by regressing time spent per reappraisal on reappraisal quality.",
    "We included random intercepts for vignette, reappraiser, and rater.",
    "We found that among human reappraisers, longer time spent on reappraisal was associated with higher quality (Table 1).",
    "Because time spent on producing reappraisals may be an indication of increased effort, we were then curious to examine whether incentivizing participants to produce better reappraisals would lead to reducing the gap between humans and GPT."
  ],
